data.description: Welcome to your beautiful ranch home located in Lawrenceville, Georgia. This charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home offers a thoughtfully designed layout that maximizes comfort and ease of living, all on a single level.The open concept floor plan seamlessly connects the main living areas, providing a spacious and inviting environment for both relaxation and entertainment. The primary bedroom offers an ensuite bathroom with double vanities and a walk-in closet.  Step outside and discover the possibilities of outdoor living.The backyard is a private retreat where you can relax on the patio and enjoy the garden. The community also offers swim/tennis and a playground. Conveniently located in the Meadow Trace neighborhood, this home offers easy access to downtown Lawrenceville, Georgia Gwinnett College, Coolray Field, Mall of Georgia, The Exchange at Gwinnett, Northside Gwinnett Hospital, schools, shopping centers, parks and many other amenities. Don't miss the opportunity to make the delightful home your own.
